Package: truncpois
Type: Package
Title: Truncated Poisson Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Arun", "Sundar Paulraj", email = "arun.paulraj.2026@mumail.ie", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Keefe", "Murphy", email = "keefe.murphy@mu.ie", role = "aut")
  )
Date: 2026-04-05
Description: Provides functions for the truncated Poisson distribution, including
    density (dtruncpois), cumulative distribution function (ptruncpois),
    quantile function (qtruncpois), and random generation (rtruncpois).
    Also includes functions for mean (extruncpois) and variance (vartruncpois).
